nodes.title: Prompting Note
widgets_values:
1. Start like a Midjourney prompt.
2. Render image to see results and differences between SDXL original render and SD1.5 tuned image.
3. Gradually introduce single keywords to fill-in the "imaginative gap" of the SD1.5 rendering 
(Supportive and repetitve keywords will not reduce the SDXL base render quality nor creative power)
4. ComfyUI does not normalize the prompt's keywords. It treats them equal and based on specified strength.
